snippet.title: Dragon Quest Builders 2 - Build Your Fate Together Trailer
snippet.description: Team up with friends to build together when 4-Player multiplayer heads to Dragon Quest Builders 2, available on July 12, 2019 for Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4.
